{"tid":279591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求 香港雙眼皮醫生推介","createTime":"2017-06-11T11:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:15:13.000Z","uid":89766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4440a42f8997dfcdfe21034f1b272f1c0e49b302","tid":279591,"uid":89766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"萬能的連登巴絲們<br />\n<br />\n有冇人整過or朋友整過而又整得唔錯嘅醫生推介<br />\n<br />\n我諗住7月去割<br />\n<br />\n上網search 過好多都係其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我就比較想係香港整<br />\n<br />\n其中唔知有冇巴絲聽過沈志宏醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50df4566ba4077ab1df345a14d30464b125fa91","tid":279591,"uid":89766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c62b66e813ecc9027d84e614c86ce9587180a6d","tid":279591,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"整容 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9a8581e176465254318e05fc77153678de30fa","tid":279591,"uid":89766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整容 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大把人用雙眼皮膠水膠紙喇<br />\n<br />\n我只係將佢變成永久姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc4b9ce404a1a8130a787ebd3f50121a2a867aa","tid":279591,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整容 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大把人用雙眼皮膠水膠紙喇<br />\n<br />\n我只係將佢變成永久姐